					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Just tested Visual6502 and SXA, 9E doesn't increment that high byte of the argument by 1.<br /><br />Visual6502<br /><br />DataBus = (X &amp; ((temp &gt;&gt; 8) + 0));<br /><br />What we are told<br /><br />DataBus = (X &amp; ((temp &gt;&gt; 8) + 1));</div>

					
