					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">SXA now passes all test ROMs.<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">if (low + Y &gt; 0xFF)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;low += (((high &amp; X) &lt;&lt; 8) + Y);<br />else<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;low += ((high &lt;&lt; 8) + Y);<br /><br />DataBus = (X &amp; (high + 1));<br /></div><br /><br />Thanks for the help guys.</div>

					
